text.tspan: Share of people with at least one dose of COVID-19 vaccine by age,
Share of the population in each age group that has received at least one vaccine dose. This may not equal the share that
has completed the initial protocol if the vaccine requires two doses.
Data source: Official data collated by Our World in Data (2024)
